== About ==

Semantic Tasks is an extension to MediaWiki that works in conjunction with another extension, Semantic MediaWiki, to provide email task notifications and reminders.

Notes on installing Semantic tasks can be found in the file INSTALL.

== Credits ==

Semantic Tasks was written by Steren Giannini.

== Manual ==

* Notification emails are sent when a task is created or updated. The system looks for the [[Assigned to::*]] property.

* Reminders emails. The system looks for the [[Reminder at::*]] and the [[Target date::*]] property. It then send reminders to the assignees.
You must run a cron job once a day to execute the reminder script :
php extensions/SemanticTasks/ST_CheckForReminders.php

